{"tid":2140669,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"果籽消費指南： 「中美大戰之花生醬」","createTime":"2020-08-05T07:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T11:35:37.000Z","uid":240448,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed84d54c71d53540087f1024d6cffbd450350853","tid":2140669,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wCO2PvF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwCO2PvF.png&h=40687507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n說起花生醬，Skippy這個牌子應該最出名、最多人吃，説到底都是美國品牌，當然以為是在美國製造，但原來我們平日在連鎖超市買到的，是中國製造的版本。<em><span class=\"red\">今次買來美國版和國產版，看看有甚麼不同。兩者價錢相近，成份都幾乎一樣，都是有花生、糖、鹽和氫化植物油，美國製那款成份含有氫化植物油，而中國製的就含有完全氫化植物油。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甚麼是氫化植物油呢，簡單來説就是植物油（例如花生油），在室溫中是液態，但在製作過程中要變成花生醬，就要經過一個氫化過程，即是將液態轉成固態。氫化過程是會產生兩款氫化油的，分別是完全氫化油（fully hydrogenated oil）和部份氫化油（partially hydrogenated oil），美國版雖然沒有寫明是哪一款，但通常沒有寫的，都估計可能含有反式脂肪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3HrwKC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3HrwKC.png&h=d5a9b8f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e71013229bd2c5b44b70a2425c94f7b002230d01","tid":2140669,"uid":240448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"汁： <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200804/HBMX77MDCFBRTJQBCQJDQCE4AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200804%2FHBMX77MDCFBRTJQBCQJDQCE4AA%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeaj9kuezr8BQg8uGmIe3q97E%3D&h=51137b97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200804%2FHBMX77MDCFBRTJQBCQJDQCE4AA%2F&h=7e9c7567\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200804/HBMX77MDCFBRTJQBCQJDQCE4AA/</a>"},{"pid":"5caf48e07aee5ca4b363c557b96e142e9144c053","tid":2140669,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T07:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffa3478c606114f459bd86757ed6e1707e07b9d","tid":2140669,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c948e2db381708c98dd261b6af8be21388192144","tid":2140669,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}